    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings along the door panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all basic electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it would benefit from a tune-up and some suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a reliable choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance needs.",
