      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes. It\u2019s got a few signs of love here and there, but it runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you! If you're looking for a great car that won't break the bank, you've gotta come see this one.",
