    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, well-maintained machine that has been cared for with pride. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with leather upholstery that remains supple, showing only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronic components, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has a complete service history, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of brake pads installed just 2,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts precisely without hesitation. It comes with two sets of keys and all original manuals. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
